	   <tr><td colspan=2>Iksar Monks are fun to play.  You get to explore places other's cant (not as well as rogues tho) by FDing around.  You do lots of damage but cant take hits very well.  Monks can solo longer than warriors if their equipment is good enough.<br><br>Monks have to worry about weight though.  They also can only wear a few types of armor, most of which arent anything special.<br><br>Iksar Warriors are cool as well.  Warriors can take a bunch of hits without dying but their damage output tends to be on the low side.  Iksar warriors also are rare.  Their regen makes them really good.  I'd say that iksar and ogres are the best warrior races at high levels.  The iksar AC will be higher, and they have regen.  The ogre's can't be stunned from the front, which is very important.<br><br>I'd say go with the warrior as there aren't enough of them.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
