	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hi, my advice would be to try to keep both skills maxed. I am a firm believer of always keeping skills up to thier cap for that level ... there is nothing worse then being awarded with a nice weapon of your kill and not being able to wield it with any proficiency :) This does not only pertain to weapon skills .. being that you are an Ogre you have the ability to slam as well as kick so do not neglect one for the other as each have thier uses for certain situations.<br><br>For now I would keep the 2hand up because once you get dual wield/double attack, you will find yourself using 1handers most of the time. I have found that if you negelt a skill , a good way to raise it is using it in the hell levels ( 30 35 40 etc) until it caps ... just make sure that if it is very low you only do this in a camp where your damage output is not heavily relied on ( hehehe sorry I had to laugh at that last line ;p) and be ready to switch back to your bread and butter taunt sticks.<br><br>... hope this helps.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
