	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you read warrior 101 you will have your answer to the race question.  It is just a few post below yours.<br><br>Dual Weild <br>Everytime you swing your main hand weapon (if your off hand weapon has cycled) a dice is rolled to see if you attack with your off hand weapon.  If your off hand weapon is faster then you have a change to swing it ever time you swing your primary.  If your off hand is slower, you have a chance to swing it every other time you swing your primary.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
